om\": 2941, \"to\": 2957}, {\"ngram\": \"the city's picturesque quays\", \"from\": 2958, \"to\": 2986}, {\"ngram\": \"the government\", \"from\": 2998, \"to\": 3012}, {\"ngram\": \"ambitions\", \"from\": 3041, \"to\": 3050}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier this year, the overall number of spectators was reducedto around 300,000.On Tuesday, Interior Minister G\\u00e9rald Darmanin said that 104,000 of them will be paying ticket holders with spots along the lower riverbanks, with another 222,000 watching for free from the upper banks.\", \"from\": 3053, \"to\": 3335, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3146, \"end\": 3163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Ministry_of_the_Interior_and_Community\", \"score\": 0.8901031947239363, \"rank\": 0.12154266370095453, \"text\": \"Interior Minister\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Ministry_of_the_Interior_and_Community\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Ministry_of_the_Interior_and_Community\"}, {\"begin\": 3164, \"end\": 3179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G\\u00e9rald_Darmanin\", \"score\": 0.9999999823289728, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"G\\u00e9rald Darmanin\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G\\u00e9rald_Darmanin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G\\u00e9rald_Darmanin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the overall number\", \"from\": 3072, \"to\": 3090}, {\"ngram\": \"spectators\", \"from\": 3094, \"to\": 3104}, {\"ngram\": \"reducedto\", \"from\": 3109, \"to\": 3118}, {\"ngram\": \"ticket holders\", \"from\": 3221, \"to\": 3235}, {\"ngram\": \"spots\", \"from\": 3241, \"to\": 3246}, {\"ngram\": \"the lower riverbanks\", \"from\": 3253, \"to\": 3273}, {\"ngram\": \"the upper banks\", \"from\": 3319, \"to\": 3334}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he said that the free tickets will not be available to the public via open registration as earlier envisaged, and will be invitation-only.\", \"from\": 3337, \"to\": 3479, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the free tickets\", \"from\": 3354, \"to\": 3370}, {\"ngram\": \"the public\", \"from\": 3396, \"to\": 3406}, {\"ngram\": \"open registration\", \"from\": 3411, \"to\": 3428}, {\"ngram\": \"invitation\", \"from\": 3463, \"to\": 3473}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To manage crowd movement, we can not tell everyone to come,\\\" Darmanin said.\", \"from\": 3481, \"to\": 3557, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"crowd movement\", \"from\": 3492, \"to\": 3506}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 3524, \"to\": 3532}, {\"ngram\": \"Darmanin\", \"from\": 3543, \"to\": 3551}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For security reasons that everyone understands, notably the terrorist threat of recent weeks, we are obliged to make it free but contained.\\\"\", \"from\": 3558, \"to\": 3699, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"security reasons\", \"from\": 3563, \"to\": 3579}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 3585, \"to\": 3593}, {\"ngram\": \"notably the terrorist threat\", \"from\": 3607, \"to\": 3635}, {\"ngram\": \"recent weeks\", \"from\": 3639, \"to\": 3651}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This means that tourists from France or elsewhere, as well as ordinary Parisians, will not be able to sign up for free access.\", \"from\": 3701, \"to\": 3827, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3731, \"end\": 3737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9989813843727254, \"rank\": 0.0009165344101826996, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tourists\", \"from\": 3717, \"to\": 3725}, {\"ngram\": \"ordinary Parisians\", \"from\": 3763, \"to\": 3781}, {\"ngram\": \"free access\", \"from\": 3815, \"to\": 3826}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, access to the ceremony will be allocated via quotas to select residents of towns or regions hosting Olympic events, local sports federations and others chosen by organizers or their partners, said two Interior Ministry officials.\", \"from\": 3828, \"to\": 4066, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4038, \"end\": 4055, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Ministry_of_the_Interior_and_Community\", \"score\": 0.898712255407929, \"rank\": 0.11270319724998755, \"text\": \"Interior Ministry\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Ministry_of_the_Interior_and_Community\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Ministry_of_the_Interior_and_Community\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 3837, \"to\": 3843}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 3847, \"to\": 3859}, {\"ngram\": \"quotas\", \"from\": 3882, \"to\": 3888}, {\"ngram\": \"residents\", \"from\": 3899, \"to\": 3908}, {\"ngram\": \"towns\", \"from\": 3912, \"to\": 3917}, {\"ngram\": \"regions\", \"from\": 3921, \"to\": 3928}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic events\", \"from\": 3937, \"to\": 3951}, {\"ngram\": \"local sports federations\", \"from\": 3953, \"to\": 3977}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 3982, \"to\": 3988}, {\"ngram\": \"organizers\", \"from\": 3999, \"to\": 4009}, {\"ngram\": \"their partners\", \"from\": 4013, \"to\": 4027}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The officials were not authorized to be publicly named according to ministry policy.\", \"from\": 4067, \"to\": 4151, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The officials\", \"from\": 4067, \"to\": 4080}, {\"ngram\": \"ministry policy\", \"from\": 4135, \"to\": 4150}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those invited will then need to undergo security checks and will receive QR codes to pass security barriers.\", \"from\": 4155, \"to\": 4263, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"security checks\", \"from\": 4195, \"to\": 4210}, {\"ngram\": \"QR codes\", \"from\": 4228, \"to\": 4236}, {\"ngram\": \"security barriers\", \"from\": 4245, \"to\": 4262}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Local town councils can invite \\\"their employees, kids from local soccer clubs and their parents,\\\" for example, Darmanin said.\", \"from\": 4265, \"to\": 4390, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Local town councils\", \"from\": 4265, \"to\": 4284}, {\"ngram\": \"their employees\", \"from\": 4297, \"to\": 4312}, {\"ngram\": \"kids\", \"from\": 4314, \"to\": 4318}, {\"ngram\": \"local soccer clubs\", \"from\": 4324, \"to\": 4342}, {\"ngram\": \"their parents\", \"from\": 4347, \"to\": 4360}, {\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 4367, \"to\": 4374}, {\"ngram\": \"Darmanin\", \"from\": 4376, \"to\": 4384}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the Interior Ministry officials said that sports federations could invite foreigners as part of their quotas, and towns could offer spots to people with disabilities or in a situation of need, to ''diversify\\u2033 access.\", \"from\": 4391, \"to\": 4614, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4402, \"end\": 4419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Ministry_of_the_Interior_and_Community\", \"score\": 0.898712255407929, \"rank\": 0.11270319724998755, \"text\": \"Interior Ministry\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Ministry_of_the_Interior_and_Community\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Ministry_of_the_Interior_and_Community\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sports federations\", \"from\": 4440, \"to\": 4458}, {\"ngram\": \"foreigners\", \"from\": 4472, \"to\": 4482}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 4486, \"to\": 4490}, {\"ngram\": \"their quotas\", \"from\": 4494, \"to\": 4506}, {\"ngram\": \"towns\", \"from\": 4512, \"to\": 4517}, {\"ngram\": \"spots\", \"from\": 4530, \"to\": 4535}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 4539, \"to\": 4545}, {\"ngram\": \"disabilities\", \"from\": 4551, \"to\": 4563}, {\"ngram\": \"a situation\", \"from\": 4570, \"to\": 4581}, {\"ngram\": \"need\", \"from\": 4585, \"to\": 4589}, {\"ngram\": \"diversify\\u2033 access\", \"from\": 4596, \"to\": 4613}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The official said the change was not aimed at punishing tourists, and that the Games remain more open than any Olympics in several years.\", \"from\": 4616, \"to\": 4753, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The official\", \"from\": 4616, \"to\": 4628}, {\"ngram\": \"the change\", \"from\": 4634, \"to\": 4644}, {\"ngram\": \"tourists\", \"from\": 4672, \"to\": 4680}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 4691, \"to\": 4700}, {\"ngram\": \"any Olympics\", \"from\": 4723, \"to\": 4735}, {\"ngram\": \"several years\", \"from\": 4739, \"to\": 4752}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another 200,000 people are expected to watch the opening from inside apartments or buildings overlooking the river, and about 50,000 from fan zones, Darmanin said.\", \"from\": 4754, \"to\": 4917, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Another 200,000 people\", \"from\": 4754, \"to\": 4776}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening\", \"from\": 4799, \"to\": 4810}, {\"ngram\": \"inside apartments\", \"from\": 4816, \"to\": 4833}, {\"ngram\": \"buildings\", \"from\": 4837, \"to\": 4846}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 4859, \"to\": 4868}, {\"ngram\": \"fan zones\", \"from\": 4892, \"to\": 4901}, {\"ngram\": \"Darmanin\", \"from\": 4903, \"to\": 4911}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 organizers would not comment on the shift, deferring questions to the government.\", \"from\": 4919, \"to\": 5011, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"organizers\", \"from\": 4930, \"to\": 4940}, {\"ngram\": \"the shift\", \"from\": 4962, \"to\": 4971}, {\"ngram\": \"questions\", \"from\": 4983, \"to\": 4992}, {\"ngram\": \"the government\", \"from\": 4996, \"to\": 5010}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Darmanin said the decision was made under the authority of President Emmanuel Macron, in conjunction with local officials and the organizing committee.\", \"from\": 5012, \"to\": 5163, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5081, \"end\": 5096, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Darmanin\", \"from\": 5012, \"to\": 5020}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 5026, \"to\": 5038}, {\"ngram\": \"the authority\", \"from\": 5054, \"to\": 5067}, {\"ngram\": \"conjunction\", \"from\": 5101, \"to\": 5112}, {\"ngram\": \"local officials\", \"from\": 5118, \"to\": 5133}, {\"ngram\": \"the organizing committee\", \"from\": 5138, \"to\": 5162}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With France on high alert, Darmanin said that intelligence services have not identified a specific plot targeting the Olympics.\", \"from\": 5165, \"to\": 5292, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5170, \"end\": 5176, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9989813843727254, \"rank\": 0.0009165344101826996, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"high alert\", \"from\": 5180, \"to\": 5190}, {\"ngram\": \"Darmanin\", \"from\": 5192, \"to\": 5200}, {\"ngram\": \"intelligence services\", \"from\": 5211, \"to\": 5232}, {\"ngram\": \"a specific plot\", \"from\": 5253, \"to\": 5268}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 5279, \"to\": 5291}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he said that there are multiple potential threats, including from Islamic extremist groups, violent environmental activists and ultra-right groups, as well as cyberattacks from Russia or other adversaries.\", \"from\": 5293, \"to\": 5502, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5363, \"end\": 5387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_extremism\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Islamic extremist groups\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_extremism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_extremism\"}, {\"begin\": 5474, \"end\": 5480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999999989831849, \"rank\": 8.674303618623547e-10, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"multiple potential threats\", \"from\": 5320, \"to\": 5346}, {\"ngram\": \"violent environmental activists\", \"from\": 5389, \"to\": 5420}, {\"ngram\": \"ultra-right groups\", \"from\": 5425, \"to\": 5443}, {\"ngram\": \"cyberattacks\", \"from\": 5456, \"to\": 5468}, {\"ngram\": \"other adversaries\", \"from\": 5484, \"to\": 5501}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France was hit by awave of deadly attackslinked to the Islamic State group in 2015-16 that targeted the Bataclan concert hall and other public venues, and the country has seen occasional extremist violence in the years since.\", \"from\": 5504, \"to\": 5729, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5504, \"end\": 5510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9989813843727254, \"rank\": 0.0009165344101826996, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 5559, \"end\": 5572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State\", \"score\": 0.9999999999649845, \"rank\": 2.3142211769302837e-11, \"text\": \"Islamic State\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State\"}, {\"begin\": 5608, \"end\": 5616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/November_2015_Paris_attacks\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7658700812623528e-47, \"text\": \"Bataclan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/November_2015_Paris_attacks\", \"dbped